source.query:
WITH DistinctRecords AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT "Record_ID"
    FROM "RAW".OP_DTL_RSRCH
)
SELECT 
    "RAW"."OP_DTL_RSRCH"."Applicable_Manufacturer_or_Applicable_GPO_Making_Payment_ID",
    "RAW"."OP_DTL_RSRCH"."Applicable_Manufacturer_or_Applicable_GPO_Making_Payment_Name",
    "RAW"."OP_DTL_RSRCH"."Applicable_Manufacturer_or_Applicable_GPO_Making_Payment_State",
    "RAW"."OP_DTL_RSRCH"."Applicable_Manufacturer_or_Applicable_GPO_Making_Payment_Country",
    "RAW"."OP_DTL_RSRCH"."Record_ID"
FROM 
    "RAW"."OP_DTL_RSRCH"
INNER JOIN 
    DistinctRecords
ON 
    "RAW"."OP_DTL_RSRCH"."Record_ID" = DistinctRecords."Record_ID";
